</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1452,2585,1000,1033]" pageId="47" pageNumber="326" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="47.[1450,2659,724,1231]" box="[1452,2585,1000,1033]" pageId="47" pageNumber="326">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1452,1586,1000,1033]" pageId="47" pageNumber="326">Breeding.</emphasis>
A female 
<taxonomicName authority="Mountain Vole" authorityName="Mountain Vole" box="[1732,2025,1000,1033]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="47" pageNumber="326" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="irene">Irene Mountain Vole</taxonomicName>
captured in August had three embryos.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
